# Modification

add content to ${HADOOP_HOME}/etc/hadoop/hdfs-site.xml

```
<property><name>dfs.client.block.write.replace-datanode-on-failure.enable</name><value>true</value></property>
<property><name>dfs.client.block.write.replace-datanode-on-failure.policy</name><value>NEVER</value></property>
```